popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"vignette","QuestionID":"QID1","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionJS":false,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1BJC5tq7iCTDLpk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID24","SecondaryAttribute":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">This campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/p>","QuestionJS":false,"DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"vignette2","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID24"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1BJC5tq7iCTDLpk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID25","SecondaryAttribute":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden students' perspectives. By delving into the lives of these individuals, we hope to provide students with unique insights into the challenges, strategies, and mindsets that led to success in various fields.<br>\n<br>\nThis campaign aims to foster a culture of learning and aspiration, and encourage students to envision and pursue their own paths to success.<\/span><p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>On the next page, you will see a set of 25 biographies. We will ask you to select a subset of these biographies that you believe would be of broad interest to students and are therefore ideal to feature in our campaign.<p dir=\"ltr\"><\/p>","QuestionJS":false,"DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"vignette3","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We are launching a campaign on campus to promote popular and inspirational biographies to broaden...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID25"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1BJC5tq7iCTDLpk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID26","SecondaryAttribute":"We are preparing a campaign on Facebook, marketing a set of popular and inspirational biographica...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">We are preparing a campaign on Facebook, marketing a set of popular and inspirational biographical films. Such films provide important educational content and our mission is to draw more viewers to these kinds of movies.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">The purpose of this HIT is to help us identify a set of biographical films that are widely admired and therefore the right set to feature in our Facebook campaign. We appreciate your help with this selection task in advance.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#95a5a6;\">On the next page you will see a set of 25 biographical films. We will ask you to select a subset of these films that you believe would be of broad interest to audiences and are therefore ideal to feature in our Facebook campaign.<\/span><br>\n<br>\nTo provide extra motivation to take this seriously, we\u2019ll send you a $5 bonus if your list is selected (there will be an eventual vote on all of the lists generated).<\/p>","QuestionJS":false,"DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"vignette4","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We are preparing a campaign on Facebook, marketing a set of popular and inspirational biographica...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID26"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1BJC5tq7iCTDLpk","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID16","SecondaryAttribute":"What is the highest level of school you have completed or the highest degree you have received? ","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4,5,6],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Less than high school degree"},"2":{"Display":"High school graduate (high school diploma or equivalent including GED)"},"3":{"Display":"Some college but no degree"},"4":{"Display":"Associate degree in college (2-year)"},"5":{"Display":"Bachelor's degree in college (4-year)"},"6":{"Display":"Advanced